<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221927>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Phallocryptus spinosa (Milne-Edwards, 1840). from Laguna de Gallocanta (Zaragoza, Spain). Specimens in MA Collection. Male: A, head, lateral view; B, frontal appendages; C – D, labrum, lateral and ventral views; E, second antennamere; F, second genital segment, ventral view, with eversible portion of gonopods folded inside; G, basal portion of left gonopod; H, everted gonopod. Female: I, head, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221927/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

